import { Typography } from "@mui/material"
import {FullScreenContainer ,StyledInput,StyledText
    ,StyledTextField,StyledBottomText,StyledLink,StyledButton} from "../common/loginsignupstyles"
  import { StyledTypography,StyledPaper ,StyledForm, StyledBottom } from "./verifypage.styles"
  import useParams  from "react"
export const Verify=()=>{
    const { content } = useParams<{ content: string }>();
    return  <FullScreenContainer>
        <StyledPaper>
            <StyledForm>
                <StyledTypography>
                    Verify your Phone Number
                </StyledTypography>
                <StyledBottom>
                Enter the OTP sent on 
                </StyledBottom>
                 
            </StyledForm>
        </StyledPaper>
    </FullScreenContainer>
}
